CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1777572671
OL,3,CParty leaders visit the south in final
OL,4,Cweek of election campaign
OL,6,FWhen asked if that meant he would rule
OL,7,Fout Reform councillors going into a
OL,8,Fcoalition with Conservatives on the
OL,9,Fcounty council, he said: "Let's just
OL,10,Fget the election out of the way shall
OL,11,Fwe.
OL,13,F"I don't want to speculate about doing
OL,14,Fanything after May the 7th. I'm here
OL,15,Fwith our candidate team. We're running
OL,16,Fto the line.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,412,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1777572671
OL,3,CParty leaders visit the south in final
OL,4,Cweek of election campaign
OL,6,F"You know, I do not think that
OL,7,Fcoalitions with the Conservatives are
OL,8,Fdesirable because I don't really trust
OL,9,Fthem, particularly after the last five
OL,10,Fyears they had in government."
OL,12,FHe added: "I think we've got real,
OL,13,Freal opportunities. I think there are
OL,14,Fparts of East Sussex and parts of West
OL,15,FSussex in which we're going to do
OL,16,Fvery, very well."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,412,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1777572671
OL,3,CParty leaders visit the south in final
OL,4,Cweek of election campaign
OL,6,FWhen speaking about Hampshire, the
OL,7,FReform leader said: "I mean, if you
OL,8,Flook at the polling in Hampshire, I
OL,9,Fmean literally right at this minute
OL,10,Fwith a week to go it's spin a coin for
OL,11,Fwho wins. So there's a lot to play
OL,12,Ffor."
OL,14,FWorthing Borough Council and Adur
OL,15,FDistrict Council are both Labour run
OL,16,Fat present.
OL,18,FWorthing West Labour MP, Beccy Cooper,
OL,19,Fwas asked if her councillors might
OL,20,Fhave to do a deal with the Greens to
OL,21,Fkeep control of both authorities.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,412,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1777572671
OL,3,CParty leaders visit the south in final
OL,4,Cweek of election campaign
OL,6,FShe said: "Our voters here are aware
OL,7,Fof the environmental issues we face,
OL,8,Fthe coastal erosion issues we face,
OL,9,Fthe regeneration issues we face and
OL,10,Fthey know that a progressive agenda is
OL,11,Fgoing to deliver here.
OL,13,F"So I don't see Reform as a major
OL,14,Fconversation here although I
OL,15,Fappreciate there will be some voters
OL,16,Fthere.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,412,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41106
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1777572671
OL,3,CParty leaders visit the south in final
OL,4,Cweek of election campaign
OL,6,F"I think let's see what the results
OL,7,Fare next week, we're hopeful that
OL,8,FLabour has held its votes. We
OL,9,Fappreciate that it's not going to be
OL,10,Fthe best result in the world but we
OL,11,Fare optimistic that Labour can
OL,12,Fcontinue to lead both of these
OL,13,Fcouncils."
OL,15,FMeanwhile near Petersfield, the
OL,16,FLiberal Democrat leader Sir Ed Davey
OL,17,Fvisited one of Hampshire's largest
OL,18,Fdairy farms where he drove a tractor
OL,19,Fand met farmers.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,412,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41107
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1777572671
OL,3,CParty leaders visit the south in final
OL,4,Cweek of election campaign
OL,6,FHe said: "We did very well in the
OL,7,Flocal elections last year. We beat the
OL,8,FConservatives in many parts of their
OL,9,Fheartlands and here we are in
OL,10,FHampshire where the Conservatives have
OL,11,Fa huge majority.
OL,13,F"I think people will surprised by how
OL,14,Fwell we do. We're going to make very
OL,15,Fbig gains, mainly against the Tories
OL,16,Fand stopping Reform."
OL,18,FConservative leader Kemi Badenoch will
OL,19,Fbe in the region in the coming days.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
